    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, heat a large, dry, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) over a medium heat</p>\r\n<p><strong>Once<span class=\"text-danger\">&nbsp;</span></strong>hot, add the 3 seed mix and toast for 1-2&nbsp;min or until slightly browned and starting to pop</p>\r\n<p><strong>Set</strong>&nbsp;the toasted seeds aside to cool - reserve the pan</p>",
      "order": 2,
