    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Meanwhile</strong>, top and tail, then slice your aubergine<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span> into 6 <span class=\"text-danger\">[12]</span> equally thick slices, discard the green stalk<span class=\"text-danger\">[s]</span></p>\r\n<p><strong>Season</strong> generously with salt and pepper, then coat each cut side evenly with harissa paste</p>\r\n<p><strong>Tip:</strong> this can be done in a bowl using clean hands</p>",
